summary: Since things have been going downhill so badly lately, I started watching Kati Morton’s youtube videos again (I used to watch...
body:
Since things have been going downhill so badly lately, I started watching Kati Morton’s youtube videos again (I used to watch them every week back in 2012/2013 when my ED was at it’s absolute worst. 

And it’s weird watching them again now mostly bc while I’m in a similar boat as I was back then, I don’t just have an eating disorder anymore like I did back then.. I have that still, but then I also have depression, generalized anxiety, social anxiety, and cptsd… soooo I am braching way out from just her ED videos lolol
